import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Card, CardContent } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import Theme from '../components/Theme';

const ExplorePathways = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ marginTop: 4, marginBottom: 2 }}>
        Explore Pathways
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Browse by S.T.E.A.M Fields</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Explore different S.T.E.A.M fields to find your interests.
              </Typography>
              <Button component={Link} to="/explore/fields">Explore Fields</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Search for Specific Careers or Interests</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Search for specific careers or interests within S.T.E.A.M.
              </Typography>
              <Button component={Link} to="/explore/search">Search Careers</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6">Historical Context</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                Discover the historical context of S.T.E.A.M advancements.
              </Typography>
              <Button component={Link} to="/history">Explore History</Button>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default ExplorePathways;
